br />\n唔知準唔準，但即係一年 117,934g Oxygen。即 1 日約 323g oxygen，產量比現在 MOXIE 多大約 25%。<br />\n而 MOXIE 的體積就如圖中所見：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/styles/full_width/public/thumbnails/image/moxie_being_installed_in_perseverance.jpeg?itok=xoK5GjYF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Ffull_width%2Fpublic%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2Fmoxie_being_installed_in_perseverance.jpeg%3Fitok%3DxoK5GjYF&h=78dd42a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦即係話，兩部 MOXIE 已經可以生產多於一棵樹一日產生的 oxygen。而且毅力號係太陽能供電，十年樹木，百年樹仁。咁你話你去種樹等佢生長10年，唔係死蠢會係咩野??"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3786303c7b71dfc2b750b3c0b4651db96970cc7f","tid":2499846,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"建議各位無視上面人個條叫「愛在深尻」既on9仔<br />\n佢應該係精神有問題"}}